<object id="GUID-85899270-A4B0-400C-AEDD-A10FDBCAE176" class="- topic/object "><desc class="- topic/desc "><p class="- topic/p ">Check printheads in X position </p></desc><param name="testid" value="046021" class="- topic/param "/><param name="target" value="NIL" class="- topic/param "/><param name="axmodule" value="None" class="- topic/param "/></object> 
</p></section><section id="GUID-1156E15C-FA11-42F7-80CE-F9823F371FA9" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Function</title><p class="- topic/p ">Print and scan test charts to determine the position of the printheads in X direction. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">This includes: 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Relative difference of the printhead X-position. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Contribution of carriage bearings to printhead X-position. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Smoothness of bearings and guidance with respect to media step marker measurements. 
</p><note id="GUID-78534504-D880-4B44-A6B2-F8F1C9949191" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">On the operator panel tap on the [Output]  icon. Make sure [Wind the output]  is set to [No]  
</p></note></li></ul><note id="GUID-9D8FB86C-79B7-423B-81D7-AC5FB95B4BAD" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Carry out this SDS test only on PPP S&amp;S HQ request. 
</p></note></section><section id="GUID-8B850BDF-E4F3-4353-8EA8-26E9EC89A7EC" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Description</title><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Start SDS test. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Select the media roll to use. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Press continue 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Information visible: 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Progress, Measurement errors, PH relative X, Carriage bearing influence, Yellow marker X variation. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">The test should end successfully. 
</p></li></ol></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-686678F1-A321-4B08-84D3-63C9CD28C7FA.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>SDS</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
